Fragrance: {{ $('Get Next Pending Row').first().json.fragrance_name }}
Image filename: {{ $('Get Next Pending Row').first().json.image_filename }}
Product URL: {{ $('Get Next Pending Row').first().json.product_url }}
Today's Date: {{ new Date().toLocaleDateString('en-US', { weekday: 'long', year: 'numeric', month: 'long', day: 'numeric' }) }}

=== ACTUAL PRODUCT DETAILS (use these, do NOT invent notes) ===
Top Notes: {{ $json.top_notes }}
Heart Notes: {{ $json.middle_notes }}
Base Notes: {{ $json.base_notes }}
Style: {{ $json.style }}
Best For: {{ $json.best_for }}
Brand Description (for context only, do NOT copy): {{ $json.description }}

Content angle: {{ ['GIFT', 'SEASONAL', 'OCCASION', 'LIFESTYLE', 'DISCOVERY', 'SENSORY', 'MYTHOLOGY'][Math.floor(Math.random() * 7)] }}
Title formula: {{ ['QUESTION', 'SCENARIO', 'PROBLEM_SOLUTION', 'SENSORY', 'LISTICLE', 'SEASONAL', 'GIFT', 'MYTHOLOGY', 'BOLD_CLAIM', 'CURIOSITY'][Math.floor(Math.random() * 10)] }}
Description pattern: {{ ['STORY_OPENER', 'SENSORY_SCENE', 'DIRECT_CONFIDENT', 'QUESTION_ANSWER', 'FOR_WHO'][Math.floor(Math.random() * 5)] }}

RULES:
- Title: max 100 chars. First 30 chars = hook. Include fragrance name early. Use the title formula above.
- Description: 220-232 characters. 2-3 sentences. Then 3-4 hashtags on new line. Use the description pattern above.
- Alt text: 150-200 chars. Describe image visually.
- Use ONLY the actual notes listed above. NEVER invent notes.
- Return ONLY a JSON object with pin_title, pin_description, alt_text.

